": "#OOTT | Hormuz Flow Will Take ‘Weeks’ To Resume, Largest Tanker Operator Warns – FT\n\nhttps://t.co/c8zi990bbu", "time": "04:15", "author": "LiveSquawk", "author_name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 436347, "views": 6307, "likes": 12, "replies": 0, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066740275616071785", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2066740275616071785", "text": "Strait of Hormuz flow will take ‘weeks’ to resume, largest tanker operator warns\nMitsui OSK Lines boss cautions that fleet owners need to build confidence after US-Iran deal\n#oott https://t.co/SLq5qcBcvf", "time": "04:30", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 51592, "likes": 30, "replies": 0, "retweets": 4, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066754377281396830", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2066754377281396830", "text": "US SPR crude inventories in million barrels - sour vs sweet (DOE) #oott https://t.co/sChsGsdoUp", "time": "05:26", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 3837, "likes": 35, "replies": 0, "retweets": 9, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066755543717367820", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2066755543717367820", "text": "#China’s Oil Refiners Slash Output After Crude Imports Plunge\n#oott https://t.co/4qs5nCLlVP", "time": "05:31", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 2940, "likes": 13, "replies": 0, "retweets": 5, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066807250807861282", "url": "https://x.com/CRUDEOIL231/status/2066807250807861282", "text": "Based on the SAR radar feed, flows through the SoH are still pinned at low. Let's see how many barrels actually clear the strait and start printing on the water post-Friday.\n\n#oott #iran https://t.co/h5OPjNIynI", "time": "08:57", "author": "CRUDEOIL231", "author_name": "JH", "followers": 59314, "views": 36501, "likes": 202, "replies": 10, "retweets": 15, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 13, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066814556068835681", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2066814556068835681", "text": "On Hormuz: About 118 laden oil tankers carrying roughly 75 million barrels are stranded inside the Gulf and would begin moving immediately after reopening. #OOTT #IranWar‌", "time": "09:26", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 26794, "likes": 152, "replies": 11, "retweets": 22, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 9, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066814851998273747", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2066814851998273747", "text": "This will create an immediate uptick in traffic, however this is not true normalization; it reflects trapped cargoes leaving the region rather than a full recovery of trade flows. #OOTT", "time": "09:27", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 13275, "likes": 79, "replies": 4, "retweets": 10, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066815080076046585", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2066815080076046585", "text": "Most replacement vessels are still far from the Gulf, so shipping capacity cannot be restored instantly. #OOTT", "time": "09:28", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 15052, "likes": 70, "replies": 16, "retweets": 15, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066853007699091725", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2066853007699091725", "text": "As of 15 June, confirmed crossings through the monitored Strait of Hormuz zone remained flat d/d at five, covering both commercial and non-commercial traffic. @Kpler -#OOTT", "time": "11:58", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 17176, "likes": 128, "replies": 7, "retweets": 28, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 9, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066858016545419429", "url": "https://x.com/StephenKalil/status/2066858016545419429", "text": "@ShaykhSulaiman Correct &amp; about time a POTUS called out Israel for murdering civilians. Now what are Trump, U.S.  actually going to do to stop this?  Talk is cheap. #Iran📷 #oott #com #cdnpoli #Lebanon #Gaza", "time": "12:18", "author": "StephenKalil", "author_name": "Stephen Kalil🇨🇦🇺🇸", "followers": 1373, "views": 1618, "likes": 47, "replies": 0, "retweets": 5, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066875040914637113", "url": "https://x.com/NuggetCapital/status/2066875040914637113", "text": "Oh? No reservoir damage.\n\nDidnt believe it either.\n\nRoger N-L.\n\n#oott #ongt", "time": "13:26", "author": "NuggetCapital", "author_name": "Nugget Capital Partners (NCP)", "followers": 7677, "views": 6576, "likes": 24, "replies": 5, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066881239584264440", "url": "https://x.com/IliaBouchouev/status/2066881239584264440", "text": "While #OPEC wanted to be seen as a vol manager, they benefited from vol spikes. Now not only China but also @ENERGY more prudent SPR mgmt could make oil mkt more mean-reverting (vs momentum), having funds to redo their algos.   \n#oott\nRT @JavierBlas \nhttps://t.co/WKlbCDefHM", "time": "13:51", "author": "IliaBouchouev", "author_name": "Dr. Ilia Bouchouev", "followers": 19952, "views": 3944, "likes": 19, "replies": 2, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 8, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066905480631308665", "url": "https://x.com/shippingenergy/status/2066905480631308665", "text": "VLCCs are positioning for a reopening of the Strait of Hormuz. \n\n#tankers #OOTT https://t.co/JcmfZxXfjc", "time": "15:27", "author": "shippingenergy", "author_name": "Gibson Shipbrokers", "followers": 2491, "views": 17193, "likes": 20, "replies": 1, "retweets": 6, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066924435383472181", "url": "https://x.com/avionsunantiqu1/status/2066924435383472181", "text": "Based on Israel's continued attacks in Lebanon, Iran can walk away from its MoU commitment to open Hormuz anytime\n\nStrategy - once they've got their money and a few tankers out, shut down Hormuz.\n\nAfter which someone will offer them more money to reopen it.    Then Repeat. #OOTT", "time": "16:42", "author": "avionsunantiqu1", "author_name": "Nicholas James", "followers": 1433, "views": 2660, "likes": 10, "replies": 6, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066931524323234116", "url": "https://x.com/NoamRaydan/status/2066931524323234116", "text": "Thread 1/4 \nI spoke to Reuters for this investigation into ship-to-ship transfers in the Gulf of Oman. https://t.co/X3zwK8C0pI\n#OOTT #Shipping #IranWar‌", "time": "17:10", "author": "NoamRaydan", "author_name": "Noam Raydan", "followers": 7546, "views": 4762, "likes": 15, "replies": 1, "retweets": 11, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066944627526291800", "url": "https://x.com/Amalteya3000/status/2066944627526291800", "text": "#Iran look, crack again...\nseems US has not good situation with gasoline, deisel and mb with #oil .\n\n#oott https://t.co/Ysrll7DuT6", "time": "18:02", "author": "Amalteya3000", "author_name": "Amalteya", "followers": 773, "views": 2856, "likes": 17, "replies": 5, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066980720300392560", "url": "https://x.com/JuliOnTwtr/status/2066980720300392560", "text": "API Inventory Moves 6/16 coming up shortly. \n#oott #crudeoil #API \n\nCrude expected 4.5 million draw\n\nSPR actual -8.9 million", "time": "20:26", "author": "JuliOnTwtr", "author_name": "Julianne Geiger", "followers": 8674, "views": 5677, "likes": 62, "replies": 1, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066983617402654906", "url": "https://x.com/JuliOnTwtr/status/2066983617402654906", "text": "API Inventory Moves 06/16\n\nCrude -8.33 million (exp. -4.5 million)\nGasoline +2.479\nDistillates\nCushing \n\nSPR actual -8.9 million (lowest levels since.... 1983)\n#oott #crudeoil #gasoline #API", "time": "20:37", "author": "JuliOnTwtr", "author_name": "Julianne Geiger", "followers": 8674, "views": 89595, "likes": 198, "replies": 19, "retweets": 25, "quotes": 9, "bookmarks": 11, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066984895063249152", "url": "https://x.com/JuliOnTwtr/status/2066984895063249152", "text": "API Inventory Moves 06/16\n\nCrude -8.33 million (exp. -4.5 million)\nGasoline +2.479 million \nDistillates -461,000\nCushing -1.523 million \n\nSPR actual -8.9 million (lowest levels since.... 1983)\n#oott #crudeoil #gasoline #API", "time": "20:42", "author": "JuliOnTwtr", "author_name": "Julianne Geiger", "followers": 8674, "views": 88379, "likes": 214, "replies": 26, "retweets": 48, "quotes": 16, "bookmarks": 18, "labels": null}, {"id": "2066986588295286993", "url": "https://x.com/ZmansEnrgyBrain/status/2066986588295286993", "text": "#API reported:\nCrude: Down 8.3 mm barrels (with the SPR down 8.9 mm)\n&gt;Cushing: Down 1.5 mm barrels\nGasoline: Up 2.5 mm barrels\nDistillates: Down 0.46 mm barrels\n\n#OOTT \nIf API is correct ... https://t.co/BDKoy0qxa5", "time": "20:49", "author": "ZmansEnrgyBrain", "author_name": "Z4 Energy Research", "followers": 11920, "views": 7762, "likes": 29, "replies": 2, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": null}], "top_authors_by_tweets": [{"username": "staunovo", "name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "tweets": 29, "views": 119190, "likes": 217}, {"username": "ZmansEnrgyBrain", "name": "Z4 Energy Research", "followers": 11920, "tweets": 12, "views": 27102, "likes": 95}, {"username": "avionsunantiqu1", "name": "Nicholas James", "followers": 1433, "tweets": 8, "views": 14027, "likes": 113}, {"username": "CDCapMan", "name": "CD Capital Management", "followers": 164, "tweets": 4, "views": 1221, "likes": 8}, {"username": "Amena__Bakr", "name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "tweets": 4, "views": 72297, "likes":